autocmd FileType markdown imap <silent> ,e <Esc>cc<Esc>:-1read $HOME/.vim/my_snippets/md/e.md<CR>i<C-g>
autocmd FileType markdown imap <silent> ,i <Esc>cc<Esc>:-1read $HOME/.vim/my_snippets/md/i.md<CR>i<C-g>
